important to work at the county level the

30:15.780 --> 30:17.580
state level federal level and an

30:17.580 --> 30:19.060
international level so I think there's

30:19.060 --> 30:21.400
steps each place along the way and there

30:21.400 --> 30:23.760
has to be coordination especially at the

30:23.760 --> 30:25.440
international national level. Because if

30:25.440 --> 30:29.280
