32:00.680 --> 32:03.900
more aware of it. But I think that doing

32:03.900 --> 32:07.680
projects where you have to research all

32:07.680 --> 32:10.040
different angles of an environmental

32:10.040 --> 32:12.460
problem are one of the most valuable you

32:12.460 --> 32:14.660
